OL,3,CMPs clash as they call for changes to
OL,4,Ccoronial law in response to Clonoe
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary has
OL,8,Furged "careful consideration" as MPs
OL,9,Fcalled for changes to coronial law in
OL,10,Fresponse to the inquest into the
OL,11,Fdeaths of four IRA members.
OL,13,FHilary Benn said the findings of the
OL,14,Fcoroner were "very significant", while
OL,15,FConservative former leader Sir Iain
OL,16,FDuncan Smith said soldiers like
OL,17,Fhimself "who never asked to go to
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland" will be "dragged in
OL,19,Ffront of the courts" in the absence of
OL,20,Fthe Legacy Act.
