OL,7,FLast week, Northern Ireland's
OL,8,Fpresiding coroner, Mr Justice Michael
OL,9,FHumphreys, found that British SAS
OL,10,Fsoldiers did not have an honest belief
OL,11,Fin the necessity of using lethal force
OL,12,Fwhen they shot dead four IRA men in an
OL,13,Fambush in Clonoe, Co Tyrone, in 1992.
OL,15,FFour Provisional IRA members ` Kevin
OL,16,FBarry O'Donnell, 21, Sean O'Farrell,
OL,17,F23, Peter Clancy, 19, and Daniel
OL,18,FVincent, 20 ` were shot dead by the
OL,19,Fsoldiers minutes after they had
OL,20,Fcarried out a gun attack on Coalisland
OL,21,FRUC station.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
