OL,7,FShadow Northern Ireland secretary Alex
OL,8,FBurghart said the four men killed in
OL,9,Fthe Clonoe ambush "sought to kill, and
OL,10,Fthey operated entirely outside the
OL,11,Fbounds of the law, and yet we are
OL,12,Fbeing asked to believe that the use of
OL,13,Flethal force was not justified upon
OL,14,Fthem".
OL,16,FHe continued: "I am not a lawyer, but
OL,17,Fif this is the state of the law, then
OL,18,Fthe law is an ass, and it is up to
OL,19,FParliament to change it.
OL,26,@qD@SOUvD@EO]xD@OOU
