OL,7,F"What if this had not been on the
OL,8,Fstreets of Tyrone? What if it had been
OL,9,Fon the streets of Birmingham? What if
OL,10,Fit had been in Parliament Square?
OL,11,FWould we be asking why those men had
OL,12,Fnot been arrested?"
OL,14,FMr Burghart added that the
OL,15,F"consequences of this ruling are
OL,16,Fpotentially very severe" and would
OL,17,Fmean "more retired servicemen in their
OL,18,Fdeclining years dragged before the
OL,19,Fcourts for trying to protect their
OL,20,Fcountrymen from terrorists".
