OL,7,FThe Labour Government has committed to
OL,8,Frepealing and replacing the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Troubles (Legacy and
OL,10,FReconciliation) Act which halted civil
OL,11,Fcases and inquests and proposed
OL,12,Fconditional immunity for perpetrators
OL,13,Fof Troubles crimes in exchange for
OL,14,Ftheir co-operation with a new truth
OL,15,Frecovery body.
