OL,7,FMr Benn also highlighted that the
OL,8,FConservatives Legacy Act "would have
OL,9,Fgiven those very terrorists who were
OL,10,Fkilled in the exchange of fire, if
OL,11,Fthey had survived, the ability to
OL,12,Fsecure immunity from prosecution".
OL,14,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said: "The
OL,15,FSecretary of State rhetorically asked
OL,16,Fwhether the law around inquests needs
OL,17,Fto change ` the coroner had to answer
OL,18,Ffour questions: where, when, who and
OL,19,Fhow.
