OL,7,F"He had no role in trying to answer
OL,8,Fthe question as to why, but we know
OL,9,Fwhy.
OL,11,F"Four depraved terrorists, for the IRA
OL,12,Fand their warped ideology, tried to
OL,13,Fdestroy society and kill in our
OL,14,Fcountry."
OL,16,FMr Benn said Mr Justice Humphreys "was
OL,17,Fconsidering the facts of the case and
OL,18,Fcame to an independent judgment about
OL,19,Fthem", and MPs are "perfectly free to
OL,20,Fexpress a view about what those
OL,21,Ffindings are".
