OL,7,FHe said: "If members are arguing that
OL,8,Fthe coronial system applying to
OL,9,Finquests right across the country
OL,10,Fshould be changed, because there is a
OL,11,Fvery great deal of feeling about this
OL,12,Fparticular findings that this coroner
OL,13,Freached, I think the House should give
OL,14,Fcareful consideration before it goes
OL,15,Fdown that road."
OL,17,FSir Iain said he was "astonished" by
OL,18,Fthe coroner's ruling and "getting
OL,19,Finside the head of a soldier that is
OL,20,Fworried about whether they're going to
OL,21,Fbe shot dead is a very difficult case".
