OL,7,F"The only group that will be
OL,8,Fprosecuted will be soldiers like
OL,9,Fmyself, who never asked to go to
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, who went because we
OL,11,Fwere told to protect civilians and to
OL,12,Fserve their country.
OL,14,F"They will be dragged in front of the
OL,15,Fcourts because the Government seems
OL,16,Fnot to care about them."
